00:06:07.610 --> 00:06:11.840
into would be they
think it's OK enough

00:06:11.840 --> 00:06:15.710
to build an app that works
well in their country, which

00:06:15.710 --> 00:06:17.800
could be making sense.

00:06:17.800 --> 00:06:22.830
Because if you're just going to
the local market, that's fine.

00:06:22.830 --> 00:06:25.580
But if you're going
to the global market,

00:06:25.580 --> 00:06:27.770
this is totally a
different story.

00:06:27.770 --> 00:06:31.070
