mature markets,

00:06:35.540 --> 00:06:38.920
the device situation might
be very much different.

00:06:38.920 --> 00:06:40.540
For example, I'm from Korea.

00:06:40.540 --> 00:06:42.420
Korans love big screen.

00:06:42.420 --> 00:06:44.990
We call them phablets.

00:06:44.990 --> 00:06:47.170
And the economy
could be different

00:06:47.170 --> 00:06:50.310
even if the market seems good.

00:06:50.310 --> 00:06:54.000
The purchasing power
of users are different.

00:06:54.000 --> 00:06:56.790
