Recently, the successes we
have seen in live operation is

00:10:12.410 --> 00:10:15.200
the collaboration with the IP's.

00:10:15.200 --> 00:10:18.190
This, again, is the example
from Mixi's Monster Strike.

00:10:18.190 --> 00:10:22.700
